  "instructions": [
    "Combine onion, garlic, radish, and a pinch of salt in a food processor. Process until coarsely chopped.",
    "In a large bowl, mix together breadcrumbs, parmesan cheese, eggs, and a pinch of black pepper.",
    "Add the processed radish mixture to the breadcrumb mixture and stir until well combined.",
    "Divide the mixture into 8 equal parts and shape each part into a ball.",
    "Flatten each ball into a patty shape.",
    "Heat a non-stick skillet or griddle over medium heat and cook the patties for 4 minutes on each side, until golden brown and crispy.",
    "Transfer the patties to a plate and sprinkle with chili flakes and a squeeze of lime juice.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
